import React from 'react' import Chart from '../Chart/Chart' const Expenseschart = (props) => { const chartDataPoints = [ { label: 'Jan', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Feb', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Mar', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Apr', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'May', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Jun', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Jul', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Aug', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Sep', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Oct', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Nov', vlaue: 0}, { label: 'Dec', vlaue: 0}, ] for (const expense in props.expenses) { const expenseMonth = expense.date.getMonth() chartDataPoints[expenseMonth].value += expense.amount } return (
) } export default Expenseschart
